        {
          "title": "我们已经走到 legacy code 的尽头了吗？",
          "path": "/ai-insights/have-we-reached-the-end-of-legacy-code",
          "file": "/docs/ai-insights/2026-05/18/have-we-reached-the-end-of-legacy-code.md",
